WEBVTT

18:56.040 --> 18:58.680 line:80%
Don't use that fierce woman
to pressure me.

18:58.720 --> 19:00.010 line:80%
Listen carefully.

19:00.200 --> 19:02.540 line:80%
If you don't keep me good company today,

19:02.560 --> 19:05.620 line:80%
don't expect to keep this place
running smoothly.

19:05.720 --> 19:07.910 line:80%
Mr. Wu, please mind your manners.
